Package: rcces
Version: 0.2.0
Title: Tools to Melt, Combine, Clean, and Standardize CCES Questions
Authors@R: person("Shiro", "Kuriwaki", email = "shirokuriwaki@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utility functions for analyzing and reshaping CCES dta files.
  This package is not meant for production. For better documented standard
  functions see `kuriwaki/ccesMRPprep`, `kuriwaki/ccesMRPrun`, and `kuriwaki/cces_cumulative`.
